flowchart TD
    A[Candidate action a] --> B{Does it return information?}
    B -- Yes --> I[Informational value I(a) > 0]
    B -- No --> C{Does it improve the state?}

    C -- Yes --> G[Intervention value B(a) > 0]
    C -- No --> E[No value source]

    I --> V[Compute V(a) = I(a) + B(a) - C(a)]
    G --> V
    E --> N[Likely empty activity]
    N --> NEG[If C(a) > 0, then V(a) < 0]

    V --> D{Is V(a) > 0?}
    D -- Yes --> DO[Action can be favorable]
    D -- No --> STOP[Do not treat as re-anchor]

    DO:::good
    STOP:::bad
    NEG:::bad

    classDef good fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32,stroke-width:1px;
    classDef bad fill:#ffebee,stroke:#c62828,stroke-width:1px;
